        <xsd:element name="GetProductAvailability" type="GetProductAvailabilityType" id="oagis-id-b1e79dfc6a3e48eb8c1d06d107029d3d">
                <xsd:annotation>
                        <xsd:documentation source="http://www.openapplications.org/oagis/10">The purpose of the GetProductAvailability is to enable requests of product availability data by an Order Management business application to an Available to Promise (ATP) or Production business application.  The business process scenario is the Order Management application interacting with the Available to Promise or Production application in order to determine availability of a product for the customer.

This scenario is commonly referred to as Make to Order or Build to Order.
The response to this request is the ShowProductAvailability.
</xsd:documentation>
                </xsd:annotation>
        </xsd:element>
