                                                <xsd:annotation>
                                                        <xsd:documentation source="http://www.openapplications.org/oagis/10">Is where the information that the BOD message carries is provided, in this case GetProductAvailability. The information consists of a Verb and one or more Nouns. The verb (Get) indicates the action to be performed on the Noun (ProductAvailability).</xsd:documentation>
                                                </xsd:annotation>
